'''Adarese''' was the spoken language of the [[Adarian/Legends|Adarians]], native to the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Adari]]. It consisted of a collection of tonal inflections that were easily formed by an Adarian's naturally rigid mouth.<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

